sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP Component
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key Auth
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant RAG as SimpleRAG
    participant Unitxt as UnitxtEvaluator<br/>(Local)
    participant Handler as EventHandler

    Note over User,Handler: Phase 1: Model Pre-Selection (MPS)

    User->>Exp: search(benchmark, search_space)
    Exp->>MPS: pre_select_models(benchmark_sample)

    loop For each (foundation_model, embedding_model) pair
        MPS->>OGX: POST embeddings.create<br/>API Key Bearer
        OGX-->>MPS: Embedding vectors
        MPS->>Chroma: Insert embedded chunks (in-memory)
        Chroma-->>MPS: OK

        loop For each benchmark question
            MPS->>Chroma: Query similar chunks
            Chroma-->>MPS: Retrieved context
            MPS->>OGX: POST chat.completions.create<br/>API Key Bearer
            OGX-->>MPS: Generated answer
        end

        MPS->>Unitxt: evaluate(predictions, references)
        Unitxt-->>MPS: Scores (faithfulness, correctness)
    end

    MPS-->>Exp: Ranked model pairs

    Note over User,Handler: Phase 2: Hyperparameter Optimization (HPO)

    Exp->>GAM: optimize(search_space, top_model_pairs)

    loop For each HPO iteration
        GAM->>GAM: Predict next config<br/>(GAM surrogate model)
        GAM->>Exp: run_single_evaluation(config)

        Exp->>OGX: POST vector_stores.create<br/>API Key Bearer
        OGX-->>Exp: Vector store created

        Exp->>OGX: POST embeddings.create<br/>API Key Bearer
        OGX-->>Exp: Document embeddings

        Exp->>OGX: POST vector_io.insert<br/>API Key Bearer
        OGX-->>Exp: Chunks indexed

        loop For each benchmark question
            Exp->>OGX: POST vector_io.query<br/>API Key Bearer
            OGX-->>Exp: Retrieved context chunks
            Exp->>OGX: POST chat.completions.create<br/>API Key Bearer
            OGX-->>Exp: Generated answer
        end

        Exp->>Unitxt: evaluate(predictions, references)
        Unitxt-->>Exp: Scores

        Exp->>GAM: Update GAM model with scores
        GAM->>GAM: Retrain surrogate

        Exp->>OGX: DELETE vector_stores.delete<br/>API Key Bearer
        OGX-->>Exp: Cleaned up
    end

    GAM-->>Exp: Best RAG Pattern (optimal config)

    Note over User,Handler: Phase 3: Results Reporting

    Exp->>Handler: on_pattern_found(pattern)
    Handler-->>User: RAG Pattern (JSON / KFP artifact)
